  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "b9058d0b-af70-459e-8fc3-a4cab616cc64",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Armed Dragon LV7",
      "effect": "Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned by \"Armed Dragon LV5\". You can send 1 monster from your hand to the GY; destroy all monsters your opponent controls with ATK less than or equal to that sent monster's ATK."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Dragon Arm\u00e9 LV7",
      "effect": "Ni Invocable Normalement ni Posable Normalement. Uniquement Invocable Sp\u00e9cialement avec \"Dragon Arm\u00e9 LV5\". Vous pouvez envoyer 1 monstre depuis votre main au Cimeti\u00e8re ; d\u00e9truisez tous les monstres contr\u00f4l\u00e9s par votre adversaire avec une ATK inf\u00e9rieure ou \u00e9gale \u00e0 l'ATK du monstre envoy\u00e9."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Bewaffneter Drache LV7",
      "effect": "Kann nicht als Normalbeschw\u00f6rung beschworen/gesetzt werden. Muss durch \u201eBewaffneter Drache LV5\u201c als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung beschworen werden. Du kannst 1 Monster von deiner Hand auf den Friedhof legen; zerst\u00f6re alle Monster, die dein Gegner kontrolliert und deren ATK kleiner oder gleich den ATK des auf den Friedhof gelegten Monsters sind."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Drago Armato LV7",
      "effect": "Non pu\u00f2 essere Evocato Normalmente/Posizionato. Deve essere Evocato Specialmente da \"Drago Armato LV5\". Puoi mandare 1 mostro dalla tua mano al Cimitero; distruggi tutti i mostri controllati dal tuo avversario con ATK pari o inferiore all'ATK di quel mostro mandato."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Drag\u00e3o Armado LV7",
      "effect": "N\u00e3o pode ser Invocado por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Normal/Baixado. Deve ser Invocado por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial por \"Drag\u00e3o Armado LV5\". Voc\u00ea pode enviar 1 monstro da sua m\u00e3o para o Cemit\u00e9rio; destrua todos os monstros que seu oponente controla com ATK igual ou menor que o ATK desse monstro enviado."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Drag\u00f3n Armado LV7",
      "effect": "No puede ser Invocado de Modo Normal/Colocado. Debe ser Invocado de Modo Especial por \"Drag\u00f3n Armado LV5\". Puedes mandar al Cementerio 1 monstruo en tu mano; destruye todos los monstruos que controle tu adversario con ATK igual o menor al ATK de ese monstruo mandado."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30a2\u30fc\u30e0\u30c9\u30fb\u30c9\u30e9\u30b4\u30f3 \uff2c\uff36\uff17",
      "effect": "\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u306f\u901a\u5e38\u53ec\u559a\u3067\u304d\u305a\u3001\u300c\u30a2\u30fc\u30e0\u30c9\u30fb\u30c9\u30e9\u30b4\u30f3 \uff2c\uff36\uff15\u300d\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u3067\u306e\u307f\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u2460\uff1a\u624b\u672d\u304b\u3089\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u3063\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u3063\u305f\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u653b\u6483\u529b\u4ee5\u4e0b\u306e\u653b\u6483\u529b\u3092\u6301\u3064\u3001\u76f8\u624b\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3092\u5168\u3066\u7834\u58ca\u3059\u308b\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\uc554\ub4dc \ub4dc\ub798\uace4 LV7",
      "effect": "\uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\ub294 \ud1b5\uc0c1 \uc18c\ud658\ud560 \uc218 \uc5c6\ub2e4. \"\uc554\ub4dc \ub4dc\ub798\uace4 LV5\"\uc758 \ud6a8\uacfc\ub85c\ub9cc \ud2b9\uc218 \uc18c\ud658\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \u2460: \ud328\uc5d0\uc11c \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130 1\uc7a5\uc744 \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0b4\uace0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0b8 \uadf8 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\uc758 \uacf5\uaca9\ub825 \uc774\ud558\uc758 \uacf5\uaca9\ub825\uc744 \uac00\uc9c0\ub294, \uc0c1\ub300 \ud544\ub4dc\uc758 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\ub97c \uc804\ubd80 \ud30c\uad34\ud55c\ub2e4."
    },
